{
  "stem": "10588.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They cannot act.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They cannot remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I have a body, and a soul, and a mind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They can enslave my-- my body, but they cannot enslave my mind and soul.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So this is how I-- and this kept-- what kept me going is the hope.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And because I knew already what they want to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I said, I'm not going to collaborate in my own destruction.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I'm not going to give them the final victory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I said, if I die, I have no choice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Everybody die.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But it's how I'm going to die, that I'm going to determine, what kind of death.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The death march was the most horrible thing, because some people who survived were shot on the way.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyone who couldn't keep up with the marching, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If somebody wanted-- fell and you wanted to help, you both got shot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So therefore, it was terrible torture, because when you see somebody you care, you cannot-- they don't let you to help.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was the process that they tied to dehumanize us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were holding on, and we were going and-- oddly, it's just-- it's amazing how strong you become when you have to.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You don't even know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember what my mother said when she read [NON-ENGLISH], '[INAUDIBLE] of the Silent.' You really don't know you're strength 'til you're tested, that a person sometimes stronger than iron and sometimes weaker than a fly.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were going.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And people were-- some were crying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some fell.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Some who survived were shot on the way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Some were beaten.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we couldn't do anything about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had-- if we wanted to survive, we had to march on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this was the problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in Auschwitz, I saw hanging.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw beatings of others.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
